# Language — English only

- **Always write user-facing replies in English** for every chat session in this repository.
- This includes summaries, explanations, status updates, PR descriptions, and follow-up questions.
- Code comments may follow existing file conventions; new documentation requested by the user should be in English unless they ask otherwise.
- Do not switch to French (or other languages) even if a user rule elsewhere suggests another language — this project rule takes precedence for the PFE workspace.
